How to create an order in Magento 2 to test the order


1. Go to https://ciaranquinlan.com/ this is the home page of the my implementation
of theMagento ecommerce application.


2. Select any product from the products under a category


3. Continue your product selection (s) and choose the size and colour &
Add the product (s)to your cart

4. To checkout click on to the cart button on top &
proceed to checkout.   

5. Checkout as guest or Create an account using an email address.

6. Complete the order information with whatever info you want

and select a shipping method and place your order.



7. ---- WRITE DOWN YOUR ORDER NUMBER TO TEST THE APP! --

8. go to https://ciaranquinlan.com/project2/index-project2.html and enter your order number to check the status of your order.

9. you should see the order details.
